John Russell Baird

Age : 47Linked companies :  Canadian Pacific Railway Limited -  Canfor Corporation -  Canfor Pulp Products Inc 





Summary 



Mr. John R. Baird is on the Board of Directors at Canfor Pulp Products, Inc., Canfor Corp., Canadian Pacific Railway Ltd., FWD Group Management Holdings Ltd. and Canadian Pacific Railway Co. Mr. Baird was previously employed as Minister of Foreign Affairs by Government of Canada.He received his undergraduate degree from Queen's University.



